OK I was double checking what you're doing, and I missed the most obvious thing: The `URLSessionConfiguration` is not being passed into anything, so the configuration you're correctly setting up is not being given to anything to be used. Instead of this at the very end: 

```swift
return ApolloClient(networkTransport: HTTPNetworkTransport(url: endpointURL))
```

try this: 

```swift
let client = URLSessionClient(sessionConfiguration: configuration)
return ApolloClient(networkTransport: HTTPNetworkTransport(url: endpointURL), client: client)
```

